Intro.Dlg1: Manuel...  &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; you are 20 years old and are doing nothing, only eat and drink.
Intro.Dlg2: Let him John  &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; He has helped me a lot in the kitchen.
Intro.Dlg3: Cooking is the second thing I like to do. &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; The first is to eat.
Intro.Dlg4: Well... it is time to find work.
Intro.Dlg5: My grandson: how about looking a work in restaurants ?
Intro.Dlg6: Yes, my honey. I taught you so many things in the kitchen. Now, you should go out to improve your skills.
Intro.Dlg7: OK... I will follow your ideas. &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; Tomorrow I'll apply in a course. &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; You'll see where it will go to.
Intro.Dlg8: Son, when you achieve XPERIENCE and knowledge enough, you should run a business together &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; You will be my manager.
Intro.PresentTeacher: Hello %0, I'm the Professor Burguer. &#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; You're welcome in our school. While you are learning, in the school, I'll be together in every mission.&#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; Let start to learn a bit the environment where you'll stay some hours having fun.
Intro.AvatarEditor: I suggest you start to configure your character appearance.&#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; Click in this button to perform this action.
Intro.ClickSchool: Click on the school building every time when you want to play a mission.&#60;br/&#62;&#60;br/&#62; There I'll give you lessons and challenges to practice.
